  "title": "Advanced topics should be shown at root level",
  "body": "Instead of being \"hidden\" under a click on \"advanced topics\", we should show them in the main navigation.\r\n\r\nBecause those \"advanced\" topic are actually pretty recurrent questions so it's only \"Advanced\" because of the way we implement them, not in term of actual usage.\r\n\r\nExample from the [vuejs website](http://vuejs.org/) (:pray:)\r\n![2016-11-24-153826_381x374_scrot](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/20607059/a37352f4-b275-11e6-9e13-fd4d979a76c9.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
